dc_description_s: This line data layer represents parks in Kenosha County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Kenosha_Trails_2018.gdb. [Bike and Recreational Trails For Kenosha County. This layer is periodically updated. The source is from various local governments land use comprehensive plans.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://dataportal.kenoshacounty.org/
